makes your site faster
users all around the world, but don't have servers around the world,

eg syndbey and london could have 30 Users
30 users that are accessing my server in dallas
request to site, miliseconds, round trip might v long

CDN - endpoints around the world

CDN - reduces trip, and distance to communicate

other benefit - security through obscurity

object storage is slowest in terms of read and write speeds

a CDN is a distributed network server accelerates internet content delivery by delivering temporarily stored or cached copies of website or media content to users based on their geographic location 
